20110921 11:42:18 nbsp Are you into inline speedskating? I do a semiregular Saturday skate to Winters & back, a total of 30 miles.     I typically leave no later than 7:30am, then hang around at Steady Eddys for at most an hour, then skate back.  I skate 1214 mi/hr and either on the way there or the way back (or both) I may take a few minutes break.  This is about an hour 20 minutes each way.

Yolobus #220 stops across the street from Steady Eddys at 8:30 and 9:45 and goes back to Davis, so that is an option.

Want to join me?  Contact me at ebrensi at uc davis dot edu. Or meet at Russell & Sycamore, and theres a good chance Ill be there.   I leave there at 7:30.

